  "subject": "Replace policy participant in clamp csit with http",
  "commit_message": "Replace policy participant in clamp csit with http\n\n- Clamp docker uses only http participant and sim ppnt. Policy test cases enabled only for k8s tests.\n- Export of metrics to jaeger disabled to eliminate warnings in the logs\n- Grafana health check timeout increased.\n- Fix kafka trace query for acmr that uses spring kafka\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5567\nChange-Id: I64aee1faded035b72f1c8a5c9f6a6c777017b509\nSigned-off-by: rameshiyer27 <ramesh.murugan.iyer@est.tech>\n",
